'''Irina Schrotter''' (born 1965 in [[Iași]]) is a Romanian [[fashion designer]] and [[businessperson]].<ref name="evz"/>
She studied to become a physician, but in 1990, one year after graduating, she decided to go into the fashion business. In 2008 her company employed 1,000 people.<ref>''[[Financial Times]]'', 2008-3-7, p. 2 "[http://www.ft.com/intl/cms/bb0999bc-eba2-11dc-9493-0000779fd2ac.pdf Returnees emerge to lead renaissance]"</ref> In the same year, her main brand had revenues of 3.5 million euros, but dropped to 2.5 million euros after the financial crisis hit Romania in 2009.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.money.ro/irina-schrotter-inainte-de-criza-numele-meu-valora-intre-7-si-10-milioane-de-euro_492646.html |title=EXCLUSIV MONEY.ro >> Irina Schrotter: Înainte de criză, numele meu valora între 7 şi 10 milioane de euro |publisher=Money.ro |date=2010-02-05 |accessdate=2013-07-16}}</ref> According to a 2013 article in ''[[Der Tagesspiegel]]'', she is "Romania's most successful fashion designer".<ref name="Strunz">Lisa Strunz, [http://www.tagesspiegel.de/weltspiegel/mode/designerin-irina-schrotter-der-rumaenische-modestar/7649906.html Der rumänische Modestar. Designerin Irina Schrotter], ''[[Der Tagesspiegel]]'', 17.01.2013</ref> She participated in the [[Berlin Fashion Week]] in 2012<ref>Carmen Böker, [http://www.fr-online.de/panorama/berlin-fashion-week-irina-schrotter---realistische-traeumerin,1472782,16538320.html Irina Schrotter - realistische Träumerin], ''[[Frankfurter Rundschau]]'', 2012-7-03; same article also appeared [http://www.berliner-zeitung.de/panorama/berlin-fashion-week-irina-schrotter---realistische-traeumerin,10808334,16538320.html] in ''[[Berliner Zeitung]]''</ref> and 2013.<ref name="Strunz"/>
In 2008 she ran as an [[Independent (politician)|independent]] to become mayor of [[Iași]],<ref name="evz">{{cite web|url=http://www.evz.ro/detalii/stiri/irina-schrotter-candidez-pentru-ca-imi-pasa-472418.html |title=Irina Schrotter: "Candidez pentru ca imi pasa!" |publisher=EVZ.ro |date=2007-12-20 |accessdate=2013-07-16}}</ref> but withdrew her candidacy before the election.<ref name="renunta">{{cite web|url=http://www.evz.ro/detalii/stiri/irina-schrotter-renunta-la-primarie-800523.html |title=Irina Schrotter renunţă la Primărie |publisher=EVZ.ro |date=2008-04-20 |accessdate=2013-07-18}}</ref>
